ura de los bandoleros del mar.\n|ref=harv|year= 2008\n |publisher= Barcelona: Ediciones Robinbook\n |isbn= 978-84-7927-963-9\n}}\n* {{cite book\n |last= Fusi Azpur\u00faa\n |first= Juan Pablo\n |title= Historia m\u00ednima de Espa\u00f1a\n|ref=harv|year= 2012\n |publisher=M\u00e9xico: Turner\n |isbn= 9788415427650\n |page=304 |url=https://books.google.cl/books?id=sogO4N8mMIoC&printsec=frontcover&hl=es#v=onepage&q&f=false\n}}\n* {{cite journal\n |last=G\u00e1lvez V\u00e1zquez\n |first= Maria Eugenia\n |title=Almanzor, un h\u00e9roe andalus\u00ed\n |ref=harv|year=1996\u20131997\n| journal = Philologia hispalensis\n |volume=11\n |number= 1\n |pages= 73\u201383\n| issn = 1132-0265\n |url= http://institucional.us.es/journals/philologia/11_1/art_5.pdf\n}}\n* {{cite journal\n |last=Garc\u00eda Sanju\u00e1n\n |first= Alejandro\n |title=Legalidad isl\u00e1mica y legitimidad pol\u00edtica en el Califato de C\u00f3rdoba: la proclamaci\u00f3n de Hisam II\n |ref=harv|year=2008\n| journal =Al-Qan\u1e6dara\n |volume=29\n |number= 1\n |pages=45\u201377\n| issn = 0211-3589\n |url= http://dialnet.unirioja.es/servlet/articulo?codigo=2596556\n}}\n* {{cite book\n |last= Gonz\u00e1lez Batista\n |first= Juan\n |title= Espa\u00f1a estrat\u00e9gica: guerra y diplomacia en la historia de Espa\u00f1a\n|ref=harv|year= 2007\n |publisher= Madrid: S\u00edlex ediciones\n |isbn= 9788477371830\n |page=501}}\n* {{cite book\n |last= Guerrero Navarrete\n |first= Yolanda\n |last2= Miranda Garc\u00eda\n |first2= Ferm\u00edn\n |title=Medieval: territorios, sociedades y culturas\n|ref=harv|year= 2008\n |publisher=Silex Ediciones\n |isbn= 9788477371793\n |page=455 |url=https://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN9788477371793&printsec=frontcover\n}}\n* {{cite book\n |last= Jim\u00e9nez Losantos\n |first= Federico\n |title= Los nuestros: cien vidas en la historia de Espa\u00f1a\n|ref=harv|year= 1999\n |publisher= Barcelona: Planeta\n |isbn= 978-84-08-03304-2\n |page=437}}\n* {{cite book\n |last=Kennedy\n |first= 